metadata.name: CONSTRUCT/DESTRUCT 01
metadata.description: An ever-present theme in my work is duality: light and dark, order and chaos, minimal and maximal. CONSTRUCT/DESTRUCT explores the tension between opposing forces in the world around us and the internal and external conflicts that define the human condition. Sound design by Kero | Detroit UndergroundTM.
